<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero__image-holder"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <h1>Howdy</h1>
    <p>Most folks call me Jamie<br>and I love building things on the web.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home__intro">
  <div class="container narrow home__intro-content">
    <h2 class="h1">About Me</h2>
    <p>I've been web'n it up since 2007. When I'm not cutting code:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>I'm a proud father and husband.</li>
      <li>I think <%= link_to "travelling", "https://wagabonds.family/" %> is <%= link_to "pretty important", "https://www.instagram.com/thewagabonds/" %>.</li>
      <li>I'm a rabid Big Brother fan.</li>
      <li>I love to cook.</li>
      <li>I try to be an <%= link_to "avid reader", "https://www.goodreads.com/nobodyiscertain" %>.</li>
      <li>I'm a runner.</li>
      <li>I'm a <%= link_to "music lover", "https://www.last.fm/user/nobodyiscertain" %> & <%= link_to "vinyl collector", "https://www.discogs.com/user/nobodyiscertain" %>.</li>
      <li>Stand-up comedy is my favorite.</li>
      <li>The Ice King is the most complex TV character.</li>
      <li>I pretend to be a music maker.</li>
      <li>Meditation keeps me sane.</li>
      <li>Bo Burnham: Inside</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home__dos">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="h1">Proud Work</h2>
    <div class="flex-wrap">
      <div class="home__do-box">
        <figure>
          <a href="https://kajabi.com/" target="_blank">
            <%= image_tag "kajabi-logo.svg", alt: "Kajabi", width: "100%", style: "max-width:225px"%>
          </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="do-box__about"><p>I'm currently the Engineering Manager<br>for the Build team at Kajabi. <%= link_to "We're Hiring!", "https://kajabi.com/careers#open-positions", target: "_blank" %></p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="home__do-box">
        <figure>
          <a href="https://www.dailyminded.com" target="_blank">
            <%= image_tag "dailyminded.svg", alt: "Daily Minded", width: "100%", style: "max-width:225px"%>
          </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="do-box__about"><p>I am the technical <b>co-founder</b> of <a href="https://www.dailyminded.com" target="_blank">Daily Minded</a>:<br>An online journal you might actually keep up with.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home__posts">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="h1">From the Blog</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <% blog.articles.each do |article| %>
        <div class="card">
          <%= link_to article.title, article.url %>
          <p><%= article.data.description %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
